data.description: Spacious three car garage home, easy access to city amenities.Bonus room has a closet and a sliding barn door.Heating & A/C only 3 months old, roof replaced in 2019, 16' X 45' paved patio with exterior benches.Neighborhood amenities, dues $287.00 annually., include a pool, basketball court and a second playground coming soon. Matthews elementary is a National Blue Ribbon school for academic excellence and the highly rated Nixa high school are both in walking distance.
